{"tid":2024272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"KKwong搞咗個口罩商會出嚟；係時候夾份用平價掃一堆捐俾美國、東南亞等嚴重國家","createTime":"2020-05-19T13:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T17:51:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5509958f73d2a28fa4140d9f92186c1b5e029b43","tid":2024272,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYgD7D2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYgD7D2.png&h=3c122cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/DrKKwongChem/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FDrKKwongChem%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7i3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=b5cd6042\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/DrKKwongChem/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日老燒都話<br />\n台灣應該趁哩個時候捐口罩<br />\n反正查實唔使用咁多<br />\n<br />\n查實香港都一樣<br />\n<br />\n香港都應該產能過剩<br />\n搞手都係多數求名唔係求利<br />\n有得傾吓用成本價（或多少少）<br />\n買一大堆捐俾其他國家<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n［CUP]美國醫院防護裝備嚴重不足 前線護士自白：對不起，我辭職<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2018850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2018850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef4e29beb5e36804733a64a02a3c3b177a9c11fd","tid":2024272,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"香港產能過剩？！係香港人有錢成炒價口罩咋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fca1b820cf469e63dbceaee52bf8bf692e5a550","tid":2024272,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38154e2c4ea38d22e155e9cc2b4350b22763cfd4","tid":2024272,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ef4e29beb5e36804733a64a02a3c3b177a9c11fd","tid":2024272,"uid":75823,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"香港產能過剩？！係香港人有錢成炒價口罩咋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/ass